DeutschTelekom pays an annual DiviDend of 0,70 EuRo per Share.
The "RegelBedarf" of HartzIv is 374 EuRo per month, i.e. 4488 EuRo per year.

If you would buy 6411 shares, you would earn 4488 EuRo 

The price of 2012-03-14 was 8.82 EuRo.
56549 EuRo InVest would secure your RegelBedarf (however, not considered tax).